Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Kayapa Field Hospital in the Municipality of Kayapa, Province of Nueva Vizcaya, to Lt. Tidang Memorial Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 715
An Act Changing the Name of the Kayapa Field Hospital in the Municipality of Kayapa, Province of Nueva Vizcaya, to Lt. Tidang Memorial Hospital
Section 1. The name of the Kayapa Field Hospital in the Municipality of Kayapa, Province of Nueva Vizcaya, is hereby change to Lt. Tidang Memorial Hospital.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1a\^/phi1
Approved: April 13, 1984
